For {= handheld =}+ handhelds (phones / tablets / locked-down consoles like the Switch out of scope), find current US street prices from retailer product pages — at least {= url =} different pages per handheld. Handhelds are Windows or SteamOS handheld gaming PCs.

Each page must be an actual retailer listing for that specific handheld — not a price comparison aggregator / review site with price mentions / "best deals" roundup / etc — and show a current purchasable price.

Requirements:
- The page must be for the claimed handheld model — same model AND same generation / revision (ROG Ally ≠ ROG Ally X; Steam Deck LCD ≠ Steam Deck OLED). Storage / color SKU variants of the same model and generation are okay and considered a model match.
